callee: SELECT accounts.domain, count(*) AS value FROM statuses INNER JOIN accounts ON accounts.id = statuses.account_id INNER JOIN statuses_tags ON statuses_tags.status_id = statuses.id WHERE statuses_tags.tag_id = NULL AND statuses.id BETWEEN 111350105112576000 AND 111361429733376000 GROUP BY accounts.domain ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 10
